# Store LF, check out LF — on every platform, Windows included.
# Prettier and CI both demand LF; without this, Windows' autocrlf
# rewrote files to CRLF on every branch switch/merge, causing phantom
# "modified" files and false format-check failures on untouched code
# (TECH-DIRECTION.md §4, established 2026-07-08).
* text=auto eol=lf
# Exception: cmd.exe batch files want CRLF (LF-only batch files can
# misparse labels/multi-line constructs).
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
